		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Well I decided to try dinking around and dropping an SPC-700 into my FPGA for fun, but I cannot find any of those good docs that Blargg talks about.  Google and wikipedia return docs from 1997 or so which I know are ancient and all but useless.
<br />
<br />Is there some secret document fountain I am missing?  Ideally I will be modifying my 6502 core to run the CPU and then some FPGA fun for the DSP portion itself.

		

