		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />From what I've read of the documents, the SPC700 CPU handles like a 6502. But something struck me as odd about the mnemonics:
<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">.section &quot;IPL&quot;<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; MOV X, #$EF<br />&nbsp; &nbsp; MOV SP, X</div>
<br />It looks like someone with an x86 background took out a red pen and scribbled all over a 6502 manual.

		

